-- India to Decide on Periodicity of Gasoline Price Revisions in Three Weeks
-- Rakteem Katakey
-- 2010-06-30T07:45:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-30/india-to-decide-on-periodicity-of-gasoline-price-revisions-in-three-weeks.html

          
          
             The frequency of gasoline price
revisions in India will be decided in two to three weeks, Oil
Secretary S. Sundareshan said in New Delhi today.  
